query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as total_relatorios
FROM relatorios_livres rl
INNER JOIN gestor_lojas gl ON rl.lojaId = gl.lojaId
WHERE gl.gestorId = 5 
AND MONTH(rl.dataVisita) = 2 
AND YEAR(rl.dataVisita) = 2026;
